title: Drag Race‘s Alaska Recreates a Sure to be Iconic Look from America’s Next Top Model‘s Rita Ora
text:
Drag Race ‘s Alaska Recreates a Sure to be Iconic Look from America’s Next Top Model ‘s Rita Ora Get the Rita Ora lewk in four easy steps. by Damian Bellino 4h ago 
Rita Ora serves fashion and face on each and every episode of America’s Next Top Model so its only appropriate that we get a tutorial on how you can snatch her look. Alaska Thunderfuck , winner of RuPaul’s Drag Race All Stars , has done us the great honor of taking one of Rita’s sure to be iconic looks from this week’s judging panel and expertly recreated the lewk .
